screen_desc: The screenshot shows a ride-hailing app interface. At the top, there are two main tabs: "Rides" and "Eats." Below that, there is a search bar to enter a pickup point and a button to set the pickup time. A green banner with an illustration and the text "Want better pick-ups?" is displayed. Under the "Suggestions" section, there are options for "2-Wheels," "Ride," "Reserve," and "Rental Cars," with the "Rental Cars" option marked as "Promo." The "Save everyday" section features icons related to navigation and scooters. At the bottom, there are navigation icons for "Home," "Services," "Activity," and "Account."
